veTraceImage` invocation must add the\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:371:  equivalent entry to the trace directory passed by `-PtraceMetadataPath`. The\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:431:  -PmetadataConfigDirs=<output_dir>/agent` — normal coordinate validation\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:433:- `./gradlew runNativeTraceImage -Pcoordinates=...\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:434:  -PtraceMetadataPath=<runs_dir>/cycle-<i>\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:436:  -PmetadataConfigDirs=<agent dir,accepted trace dirs>` — fallback trace-cycle\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:457:| `dynamic_access_iterative` per-class loop | After every class with a coverage gain (Resolved or PartialCommit) (§WF-dynamic-access-workflow) | `tests/src/<group>/<artifact>/<version>/build/natively-collected/<class-key>/` |\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:458:| `fix_java_run_fail` native-mode path | After the agent's final edit, as the success gate (§WF-java-fail-fix-workflow) | `tests/src/<group>/<artifact>/<version>/build/natively-collected/_global_/` |\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:478:   -PmetadataConfigDirs=<output_dir>/agent`. If the coordinate passes,\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:481:5. Each fallback outer cycle invokes `./gradlew runNativeTraceImage\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:482:   -Pcoordinates=... -PtraceMetadataPath=<runs_dir>/cycle-<i>\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:484:   `-PmetadataConfigDirs=<agent dir,accepted trace dirs>` appended whenever\\n./forge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:506:     `runNativeTraceImage` after codex.\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_26\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc \\\"find tests/src/velocity/velocity/1.5/build/native