hen run one final native-image-utils merge over\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:57:   `<output_dir>/trace` when present. The final merge result is copied to\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:160:| Output directory | Caller | Absolute staging root for this gate invocation. The caller picks a path namespaced per (library, class) for the dynamic-access caller, or per coordinate for non-class-scoped callers. The gate writes JVM-agent metadata to `<output_dir>/agent`, merged trace metadata to `<output_dir>/trace`, and writes durable repository metadata only after the final native-image-utils merge succeeds. |\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:175:  updated only by the final native-image-utils merge. On `FAILED`, staging\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:206:    Route -- 0 --> MergeTrace[mergeNativeTraceMetadata<br/>accepted trace dirs &rarr; trace_dir]\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:252:    test are sufficient. The gate runs `mergeNativeTraceMetadata` to\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:254:    runs the final native-image-utils merge over durable metadata, staged\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:373:  must match the entry later consumed by `mergeNativeTraceMetadata`; otherwise\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:382:#### `mergeNativeTraceMetadata`\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:438:- `./gradlew mergeNativeTraceMetadata -PinputDirs=...\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:441:- `./gradlew mergeNativeTraceMetadata -PinputDirs=...\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:488:   - `0` → run `mergeNativeTraceMetadata` once with all accepted run\\nforge/docs/workflows/native-metadata-tracing.md:490:     then run one final native-image-utils merge of durable metadata,\\ntests/tck-build-logic/src/main/java/org/graalvm/internal/tck/utils/MetadataGenerationUtils.java:382:                        \\\"mergeNative